You are playing a cultist in a very uncomfortable situation.
You can run by using the move buttons.
You can attack by bumping into an enemy. 
You will do as much damage as there are swords on the top bar.
Your damage will get better when you level by killing monsters.
You have a limited amount of bullets you can fire. 
Bullets fire to your right and instantly kill what they hit.
You have a limited amount of teleports you can use.
Teleports move you 2 tiles to the right, or further if that position is blocked.
You will kill a monster if you teleport into them.
You will die if you get caught by the BLACK.
You will die.
Good luck.
